He's thought to have had the most profitable
haul in pirate history when he led a small

00:04:56.840 --> 00:05:03.180
pirate squadron to overtake the Ganj-i-sawai
- the flagship of a 25 ship convoy of Grand

00:05:03.180 --> 00:05:08.620
Mughal vessels containing Â£600,000 in metals
