00:05:08.620 --> 00:05:13.240
And amazingly he's one of the few famous pirates
thought of have escaped alive with his treasure

00:05:13.240 --> 00:05:18.470
- one story saying he disappeared to Madagascar
with all of his loot and lived like a king.

00:05:18.470 --> 00:05:22.670
The other story is that he died penniless
after squandering all his money.

00:05:22.670 --> 00:05:27.710
The well-known pirate voice is an impersonation
of West Country English and Robert Newton

00:05:27.710 --> 00:05:33.000
who was born in England not far from the birthplaces
of many famous pirates played both Long John

00:05:33.000 --> 00:05:39.530
Silver and Blackbeard in early Disney movies.

00:05:39.530 --> 00:05:44.880
Henry Morgan, the man whom Captain Morgan
rum is named after was actually privateer

00:05:44.880 --> 00:05:46.110
and not a pirate.

00:05:46.110 --> 00:05:49.210
A privateer is basically a legal pirate.

00:05:49.210 --> 00:05:54.100
Morgan was allowed to attack enemy ships and
ports in exchange for sharing the loot with

00:05:54.100 --> 00:05:57.780
the crown and he was even knighted by King
Charles II.

00:05:57.780 --> 00:06:02.220
Although known as one of the greatest pirates
ever Morgan would've been offended to be called

00:06:02.220 --> 00:06:03.220
one.

00:06:03.220 --> 00:06:07.441
Parrots and monkeys were considered trophies
of the exotic places pirates visited and were

00:06:07.441 --> 00:06:10.550
often sold for high prices back in Europe.

00:06:10.550 --> 00:06:14.530
Madame Cheng was the most famous female pirate
of all time.

00:06:14.530 --> 00:06:20.970
She commanded over 300 Junks or chinese sailing
vessels with a crew of over 20k men women

00:06:20.970 --> 00:06:21.970
and children.

00:06:21.970 --> 00:06:27.390
She started out as a prostitute that was captured
by pirates, married one of them and took over

00:06:27.390 --> 00:06:28.390
his fleet.

00:06:28.390 --> 00:06:30.680
She created a code that went like this.

00:06:30.680 --> 00:06:34.270
Disobeying her or any superior meant immediate
beheading

00:06:34.270 --> 00:06:38.550
No one could steal from the public fund or
anyone that supplied the pirates

00:06:38.550 --> 00:06:44.340
All booty was presented for group inspection
- the finder kept 20% and the rest went into

00:06:44.340 --> 00:06:48.000
the public fund
Actual money was given to the squadron leader

00:06:48.000 --> 00:06:53.060
to help unsuccessful ships
And pirates could choose to marry female captives

00:06:53.060 --> 00:06:56.940
with the ugliest, unchosen ones then being
released.

